_:N308c107b811748c7b247d26e59bd1df7 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Sophie Dean was appointed Director General for Welfare and Pensions in September 2025. Before that, she was in a jobshare with Katherine Green as joint Directors General for <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> Policy.   </p>\n\n<p>Before <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr>, Sophie and Katherine were Directors General for Borders and Trade in <abbr title=\"HM Revenue and Customs\">HMRC</abbr>. They were responsible for policy and operation of the UK border for goods and delivered the major border change programme for Brexit. Sophie and Katherine joined <abbr title=\"HM Revenue and Customs\">HMRC</abbr> in August 2018 as job share Directors of Customs and Border Design. </p>\n\n<p>Sophie was previously Finance Director at HM Treasury. Prior to that she worked in a variety of policy roles in HM Treasury. </p>\n\n<p>Before joining the Civil Service, Sophie worked in the private sector.</p>\n\n" .
<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/sophie-dean> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://schema.org/WebPage> .
